{{Documentation subpage}}
<!-- Please place categories where indicated at the bottom of this page and interwikis at Wikidata (see [[Wikipedia:Wikidata]]) -->
{{High-use}}
{{Tsh|Phab}}
A template that links to a specific [[mw:Phabricator|Phabricator]] task.
== Usage ==

* {{tlx|Phabricator|T8452}} returns: {{Phab|T8452}}
* {{tlx|Phabricator|8452}} returns: {{Phab|T8452}} (still supported but not encouraged)
* {{tlx|Phabricator}} just returns: {{Phab}}
* {{tlx|Phabricator|art{{=}}y|T1234}} or {{tlx|Phab|article{{=}}yes|T1234}} returns: {{Phab|art=y|T1234}}
* {{tlx|Phabricator|T8542|Ability to edit and compare versions of SVG images.}} returns: {{Phab|T8542|Ability to edit and compare versions of SVG images.}}

== See also ==
* {{tl|Tracked}}, float-right box

== TemplateData ==
{{TemplateData header}}
<templatedata>
{	"description": "Shorthand for [[phabricator:Tnumber|Tnumber]]",
	"params":
	{	"1": 
		{	"label": "task",
			"description": "Task number or Tnumber",
			"type": "string",
			"required": true
}	}	}
</templatedata>
<includeonly>{{Sandbox other||
[[Category:Inline interwiki link templates]]
}}</includeonly>

